"
" Leader           ,      -- Press , and then the following commands>
"                  ,f     -- CtrlP vim plugin https://github.com/kien/ctrlp.vim
"                  ,z     -- ZoomWin
"                  ,jpp   -- Pretty-prints the (currently selected) JSON
